title: Someone Asked Cassie When Her Baby Was Due (She's Not Pregnant)
description:
People can be rude, but we couldn't believe another MOM had the cojones to ask Cassie *this* on the playground...yep, she got asked the dreaded question: When are you due? Here's the thing...she's not even pregnant.
